claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: Forest plot showing relative vaccine effectiveness (with 95% CI) expressed as percentage change for Flublok versus comparator across subgroups defined by comorbidities (cardiovascular disease, respiratory disease, cardiorespiratory disease, obesity, diabetes, any condition) and endpoints (PCR-confirmed influenza, hospitalization for PCR-confirmed influenza, hospitalization for community-acquired pneumonia). This figure presents clinical effectiveness outcomes, not data on antigenic match to WHO- or FDA-selected strains, and therefore does not support the claim
